    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 30 \u2014 RevOps Intelligence Dashboard\n\n**Env variables needed:**\n- HUBSPOT_API_TOKEN: HubSpot private app token\n- STRIPE_SECRET_KEY: Stripe secret key\n- INTERCOM_ACCESS_TOKEN: Intercom API token\n- MIXPANEL_SERVICE_ACCOUNT + MIXPANEL_SECRET\n- LEADERSHIP_LIST: comma-separated emails\n\n**GA4 setup:** Replace REPLACE_GA4_PROPERTY_ID and REPLACE_GA4_TOKEN with your actual property ID and service account bearer token.\n\n**Google Sheets setup:**\n1. Create 'RevOps Dashboard' tab with a row where row_id='LIVE'\n2. Create 'Weekly History' tab for historical logging\n3. Connect Looker Studio to the sheet as a live data source",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 420
      },
